<h1 id=3D"PROMO-ACC-ImplementationDocument-May2023-Testingnotes">Testing no=
tes</h1>
<ul>
<li><p>Validation of version number and credentials are performed on all en=
d points</p></li>
<li><p>Order related data are filtered on the customer number that is assoc=
iated to the web user</p></li>
<li><p>Usage of the web service validator tool will provide a validation re=
sult on whether the response is properly form</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Typically validation issues are due to namespace mismatches</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Progress has limitations when writing the temp tables to XML: string=
 manipulation code statements exist in the finally block of most endpoint p=
rograms. May require tweaking to resolve validator issues</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>When testing, this should be verified so that it says =E2=80=9C<em>T=
he XML response is valid.</em>=E2=80=9D. When it doesn=E2=80=99t it=E2=80=
=99s either that the response is not compliant with the spec or that there=
=E2=80=99s an imperfection in the xsd files. Regardless, this should be res=
olved in order to be as compliant as possible</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Toggle on the web control option <code>promoStandard_Debug</code> to=
 have additional logging</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 id=3D"PROMO-ACC-ImplementationDocument-May2023-DataSetup">Data Setup</h=
1>
<ul>
<li><p>Security</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Security Group - PROMO</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-c=
enter" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"b692ba0aca708f0849fc4dbd6f88762b" data-image=
