image-20220609-183215.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1684758133690&=
amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"548" data-width=3D"1166" =
data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"2975825985" =
data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment"=
 data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20220609-183215.png" data-base=
-url=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-ty=
pe=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"2975825921" data-link=
ed-resource-container-version=3D"2" data-media-id=3D"7d496657-d1af-4c68-a4b=
4-63a4237e8893" data-media-type=3D"file" width=3D"468" height=3D"219"></spa=
n></li>
<li><p>Program Security - ScreenID: PromoStandard, Program: PromoStandard</=
p></li>
<li><p>Web User - Username: fdm4, Password: password, Customer: 10002902 (J=
<a href=3D"http://JiffyShirts.com" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow"=
>iffyShirts.com)</a><br>A valid web user for each customer must be created =
in order to connect to and use the Promo Standards API=E2=80=99s. User =E2=
=80=98fdm4=E2=80=99 exists in TEST and can be used as a sample. </p><span c=
lass=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper"><img class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"66d81ea=
81fab1ee178d76d2674100e40" data-image-src=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.net/=
wiki/download/attachments/2975825921/image-20220609-183254.png?version=3D1&=
amp;modificationDate=3D1684758133834&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" dat=
a-height=3D"645" data-width=3D"1165" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" da=
ta-linked-resource-id=3D"2975825988" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" dat=
a-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D=
"image-20220609-183254.png" data-base-url=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.net/=
wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-=
container-id=3D"2975825921" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"2" da=
ta-media-id=3D"57dfc2ee-3ffe-448d-9dba-f6d0e3b0cece" data-media-type=3D"fil=
e" width=3D"468" height=3D"259"></span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>External Carrier Xref <br>If an exact carrier code is not passed in =
the sendPO call, the customer can send a generic carrier description like =
=E2=80=98UPS=E2=80=99. Delta will need to setup an External Carrier Xref re=
cord so the system knows what ERP carrier to use. External Carrier (UPS) &g=
t; Carrier (UPS Ground Comm)</p>
<ul>
<li><p>There are currently 3 sample records on TEST as shown below. </p><sp=
an class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper"><img cla=
ss=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"3ec57=
1596664aa65a9d978ef32dc797d" data-image-src=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.ne=
t/wiki/download/attachments/2975825921/image-20220609-183459.png?version=3D=
1&amp;modificationDate=3D1684758134043&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" d=
ata-height=3D"338" data-width=3D"1686" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" =
data-linked-resource-id=3D"2975825991" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" d=
ata-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=
=3D"image-20220609-183459.png" data-base-url=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.n=
et/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resour=
ce-container-id=3D"2975825921" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"2"=
 data-media-id=3D"b65e0a67-09b7-42da-a46f-2262106040a1" data-media-type=3D"=
file" width=3D"468" height=3D"93"></span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>EASI 850 Record - To Control Incoming Orders<br>In order to have som=
e control over incoming PROMO orders, we required a record in the EASI 850 =
table. To clarify, this is unrelated to EASI 850 functionality, but the rec=
ord just needs to exist primarily to govern active and auto release as it r=
elates to PROMO Standards. The web user will be attached to the customer nu=
mber and therefore the PROMO Standards order import will reference the cust=
omer number to the EASI records Partner ID. </p><span class=3D"confluence-e=
mbedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper"><img class=3D"confluence-embedde=
d-image image-center" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"15e9af73ef8fb515f5ed7dbb2676d=
43b" data-image-src=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachme=
nts/2975825921/image-20220802-195253.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=
=3D1684758132512&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"709" dat=
a-width=3D"1579" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-i=
d=3D"2975825961" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-ty=
pe=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20220802-1952=
53.png" data-base-url=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-re=
source-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"2975=
825921" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"2" data-media-id=3D"815c8=
8f3-6f56-4b6e-902d-594cd28a2ad6" data-media-type=3D"file" width=3D"468" hei=
ght=3D"210"></span></li>
<li><p>Web Options<br>There are various web options that dictate the operat=
ion and use of the Promo Standards API and end results. They are found in t=
he =E2=80=98Web Control=E2=80=99 program under the =E2=80=98Options=E2=80=
=99 tab. Below are the options that directly impact key factors with incomi=
ng orders and inventory.</p>
<ul>
<li><p>promoStandard_cancelReason: PS</p></li>
<li><p>promoStandard_gZipJINV: Enabled</p></li>
<li><p>promoStandard_holdTime: 15</p></li>
<li><p>promoStandard_InvPercent: 90</p></li>
<li><p>promoStandard_shipWhseList: A1, J1, K1, L1, T1, V1, and X1 (refer to=
 test environment for full json)</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file=
-wrapper image-center-wrapper"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image imag=
e-center" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"770a823f26603808d2690dfbe50d52f8" data-im=
age-src=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/29758259=
21/image-20220609-183908.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D16847581341=
93&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"701" data-width=3D"140=
2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"297582599=
4" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachme=
nt" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20220609-183908.png" data-b=
ase-url=3D"https://fdm4inc.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content=
-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"2975825921" data-l=
inked-resource-container-version=3D"2" data-media-id=3D"84bb10e2-0bc9-454a-=
831b-99270e5f3de5" data-media-type=3D"file" width=3D"468" height=3D"234"></=
span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Inventory Flat File</p>
<ul>
<li><p>EASI Document - Document Code: JINV, Partner ID: 10002902 (refer to =
test environment for full details)</p></li>
<li><p>Prepared script file: <code>/u/test/code/scripts/promostd_process_te=
st.sh</code></p>
<ul>
<li><p>Removed ^M</p></li>
<li><p>Allowed execute permission</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Cronjob setup (testadm user): <code>1-23 * * * /u/test/code/scripts/=
promostd_process_test.sh &gt;&gt; /u/test/logs/promostd_process_test.log 2&=
gt;&amp;1</code></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h1 id=3D"PROMO-ACC-ImplementationDocument-May2023-Questions">Questions</h1=
>
