</ul></li>
<li><p>Validator sample</p>
<ul>
<li>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;Get=
ConfigurationAndPricingRequest xmlns:xsi=3D"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchem=
a-instance" xmlns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PricingAndConfigura=
tion/1.0.0/"&gt;
  &lt;wsVersion xmlns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PricingAndConfi=
guration/1.0.0/SharedObjects/"&gt;1.0.0&lt;/wsVersion&gt;
  &lt;id xmlns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PricingAndConfiguratio=
n/1.0.0/SharedObjects/"&gt;fdm4&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;password xmlns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PricingAndConfig=
uration/1.0.0/SharedObjects/"&gt;password&lt;/password&gt;
  &lt;productId xmlns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PricingAndConfi=
guration/1.0.0/SharedObjects/"&gt;012G&lt;/productId&gt;
  &lt;priceType xmlns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PricingAndConfi=
guration/1.0.0/SharedObjects/"&gt;Customer&lt;/priceType&gt;
  &lt;currency xmlns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PricingAndConfig=
uration/1.0.0/SharedObjects/"&gt;USD&lt;/currency&gt;
&lt;/GetConfigurationAndPricingRequest&gt;</pre>=20
</div>
</div><p></p></li>
<li><p>There seems to be a bug in the validator tool that always sends in =
=E2=80=9CAFA=E2=80=9D as the currency when <code>&lt;fobId&gt;</code> is su=
pplied and then fails validation</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Additional test cases</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Validation on <code>productId</code> for valid style number</p></li>
<li><p>Filter on <code>&lt;partId&gt;</code></p>
<ul>
<li><p>Validation on <code>partId</code> for active item number</p></li>
<li><p>Could also act as a color filter if the value instead matches a <cod=
e>color-code</code> for the given style</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Validation on <code>&lt;fobId&gt;</code> for valid warehouse</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Uses web control option <code>promoStandard_primaryWhse</code> when =
not supplied</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Supply alternative <code>&lt;priceType</code> among <code>{Customer,=
 List, Net }</code></p></li>
<li><p>Verify data returned in accordance with web control option <code>pro=
moStandard_useCCPricing</code></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p></p>
