<h2 id=3D"PROMO-ACC-ImplementationDocument-May2023-sendPO()">sendPO()</h2>
<ul>
<li><p>SoapUI sample</p>
<ul>
<li>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">&lt;soa=
penv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv=3D"http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" x=
mlns:ns=3D"http://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PO/1.0.0/" xmlns:shar=3D"http=
://www.promostandards.org/WSDL/PO/1.0.0/SharedObjects/"&gt;
   &lt;soapenv:Header/&gt;
   &lt;soapenv:Body&gt;
      &lt;ns:SendPORequest&gt;
         &lt;wsVersion&gt;1.0.0&lt;/wsVersion&gt;
         &lt;id&gt;fdm4&lt;/id&gt;
         &lt;password&gt;password&lt;/password&gt;
         &lt;ns:PO&gt;
            &lt;ns:orderType&gt;Blank&lt;/ns:orderType&gt;
            &lt;ns:orderNumber&gt;CustomerPoNumber&lt;/ns:orderNumber&gt;
            &lt;ns:orderDate&gt;2022-04-04&lt;/ns:orderDate&gt;
            &lt;ns:totalAmount&gt;226.80&lt;/ns:totalAmount&gt;
            &lt;currency&gt;USD&lt;/currency&gt;
            &lt;ns:LineItemArray&gt;
               &lt;ns:LineItem&gt;
                  &lt;ns:lineNumber&gt;1&lt;/ns:lineNumber&gt;
                  &lt;lineItemTotal&gt;123.84&lt;/lineItemTotal&gt;
                  &lt;Quantity&gt;
                     &lt;uom&gt;EA&lt;/uom&gt;
                     &lt;value&gt;72&lt;/value&gt;
                  &lt;/Quantity&gt;
                  &lt;ns:PartArray&gt;
                     &lt;Part&gt;
                        &lt;ns:partId&gt;11730E27M&lt;/ns:partId&gt;
                        &lt;Quantity&gt;
                           &lt;uom&gt;EA&lt;/uom&gt;
                           &lt;value&gt;72&lt;/value&gt;
                        &lt;/Quantity&gt;
                     &lt;/Part&gt;
                  &lt;/ns:PartArray&gt;
               &lt;/ns:LineItem&gt;
            &lt;/ns:LineItemArray&gt;
            &lt;ns:ShipmentArray&gt;
               &lt;Shipment&gt;
                  &lt;FreightDetails&gt;
                     &lt;carrier&gt;GROUND&lt;/carrier&gt;
                     &lt;service&gt;UPS&lt;/service&gt;
                  &lt;/FreightDetails&gt;
                  &lt;ShipTo&gt;
                     &lt;ContactDetails&gt;
                        &lt;address1&gt;5320 OLEANDER DR&lt;/address1&gt;
                        &lt;city&gt;WILMINGTON&lt;/city&gt;
                        &lt;region&gt;NC&lt;/region&gt;
                        &lt;postalCode&gt;28403-5810&lt;/postalCode&gt;
                        &lt;country&gt;US&lt;/country&gt;
                     &lt;/ContactDetails&gt;
                     &lt;shipmentId&gt;1&lt;/shipmentId&gt;
                  &lt;/ShipTo&gt;
               &lt;/Shipment&gt;
            &lt;/ns:ShipmentArray&gt;
         &lt;/ns:PO&gt;
      &lt;/ns:SendPORequest&gt;
   &lt;/soapenv:Body&gt;
&lt;/soapenv:Envelope&gt;</pre>=20
</div>
</div></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Validator sample</p>
<ul>
<li><p>N/A - Currently not supported by the validation tool</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Testing notes</p>
<ul>
<li><p>The sample request is what is minimally needed to accept a PO reques=
t and to create an EDI order</p></li>
<li><p>Submitted orders may not be automatically released and any issues wi=
th the order will be held for manual review</p></li>
<li><p>As there are a lot of variance in the outcome of the created orders,=
 test cases should depend on the customer=E2=80=99s usage and goals. Sugges=
ted approach for successful testing is to gather PO samples from them and e=
nsure that the generated sales order contains all relevant information that=
 is in the PO request.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p></p>
<p></p>
